治犯的支持。"},{"pid":"6c9f79484287c24789745b36d60df22a50303a5c","tid":1656644,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"[掃盲]加泰羅利亞懶人包 feat. 應唔應該推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656410</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c36a3c1ebf7ff435c569f2fa0318488621362500","tid":1656644,"uid":151695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:09:01.000Z","msg":"成日話核彈都唔割 成日話殺狗都唔割 然後割頸勇士比人話係狗扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />割都割唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eaa5141b65377ff5d56008b105cfff044bf2f0c","tid":1656644,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:09:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f79a60782a5ef8572042e9fad360ae2a3747061d","tid":1656644,"uid":25412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:12:57.000Z","msg":"我唔知你地割唔割<br />\n但係我就一定不割義士"},{"pid":"440caea86ad40f9714d25c0db5ab657ba01b12ec","tid":1656644,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:13:04.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔日日抽我同父哥水 我撐cc台"},{"pid":"ca30e81caea51f30da79c120fbffd1e6fc9880df","tid":1656644,"uid":170445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76a586e2b8b907e363b3bf327b940059c7d3a384","tid":1656644,"uid":21362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca30e81caea51f30da79c120fbffd1e6fc9880df","tid":1656644,"uid":170445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"駁唔刀"},{"pid":"eb18d53b8e04fdfe6632c5551446382ada9729f7","tid":1656644,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca